reviewText: in the style of night of the demons, evil dead, and other comedy/horror/teen flicks. i don't have much expectations for current horror movies but this suprised me. one of those 'lets go to this house and party... oops its haunted by the guy your friends accidently killed' kind of movies. a real enjoyment all the way through. the one that you do not expect to survive does. VERY GOOD DONT MISS!!!!
